{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.15.1515;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\cf1\b\f0\fs20 This example shows how to validate data using the Control Verify handler.\par
\par
In this example, the First Name cannot be blank. The Last Name cannot start with 'Q'. The Salary cannot be less than $8,000 or greater than $400,000. Changes cannot be saved if they violate any of these conditions.\par
\par
The Date also has a verification, that the date should not be more than one year in the past.\par
\par
But, it is only a Warning. The user will get an irritating message, but the change can still be saved.\par
}
